{"tid":248780,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樂視大裁員】傳樂視體育最多裁7成人！","createTime":"2017-05-18T22:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T23:50:36.000Z","uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d808fa1eb37e21bddbb955ff499459b1fcee73d","tid":248780,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T22:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/19/065208_aaa3f169cf69b8e16300825e0338ea6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F19%2F065208_aaa3f169cf69b8e16300825e0338ea6c.jpg&h=7254043a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樂視大裁員，最多裁7成人！據《騰訊科技》報道，網傳多日的樂視大裁員將於今日落實，涉及樂視網、樂視控股、樂視體育等多間樂視系公司。其中樂視體育裁員幅度高達70%，由700人削減至200人。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，樂視控股體系中，市場品牌中心從100餘人減至30餘人，裁員幅度70%；銷售服務體系裁員50%，樂視網則裁員10%。而樂視影業、樂視致新（樂視電視運營主體公司）就暫未有裁員計劃。<br />\n<br />\n樂視對《騰訊科技》表示，對此沒有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56712819&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56712819%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170518&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=29ef80a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56712819%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170518&h=37c317a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56712819&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170518</a>"},{"pid":"72e28bd2db939954af7333d33d78c3187f36c38a","tid":248780,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T22:55:42.000Z","msg":"猁榮基:唉 乜咁搞"},{"pid":"d0aa1d3c0463cd716a0866ebfcd5896f6e1f6a90","tid":248780,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T23:31:39.000Z","msg":"D車唔係應該幾好賣既咩"},{"pid":"5b85f6d1d0ddfcdd33e7fdaab997e24d66cf4140","tid":248780,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T23:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}